Rihanna is without a doubt one of the world’s most successful stars, and she has made a fortune in a variety of fields, including music, fashion, and everything in between.
We don’t need to tell you that the 35-year-old has an excellent discography that spans nearly 20 years. She has released over 50 singles—just as a lead artist—and eight albums, so it shouldn’t come as a surprise that she has won nine Grammy Awards!
Rihanna has introduced a number of Fenty clothing lines asides music.. However, Rihanna made a significant foray into the cosmetics industry in 2017! She introduced Fenty Beauty, which attracted a large and diverse color palette and became an instant hit with customers.
The following year, Rihanna launched the luxuriously bold lingerie line Savage X Fenty, and in 2020, she introduced Fenty Skin!
She is able to attribute the majority of her net worth, $1.4 billion, to her makeup brand, in which she owns a 50% stake, as stated by Forbes. Wow!
