Lady Gaga
Gaga is more than just a pop superstar; She has tried her hand at many other creative endeavors in addition to her discography. From her ever-explicit music videos, we were all aware that she had some dramatic acting chops, but it was her appearance on American Horror Story that first impressed viewers: Hotel in 2015, for which she received a Golden Globe nomination for Best Actress in a Miniseries.
With her leading lady role in the hugely successful A Star Is Born in 2018, Gaga did it again. With her song “Shallow,” she won the Oscar for Best Original Song.
In 2019, she launched Haus Labs, a vegan and cruelty-free makeup line with the proud slogan “spreading kindness, bravery, and creativity.” Beyonce Beyonce
What is Beyoncé incapable of doing? From her beginnings in Destiny’s Child to her work as a solo artist that defined a generation, the 41-year-old musician has had a career unlike any other. It is evident that Beyonce is a force to be reckoned with.
The multitalented woman has put out seven solo studio albums, three visual albums, and five live albums. Before that, she had even put out five albums with her former girl group. Beyoncé ended her diet program 22 Days Nutrition in 2015, saying that it helped her prepare for her concert rehearsals.
Her introduction to wellness didn’t stop there, a year later, she introduced Adidas x Ivy Park, a fashionable line of leisure wear that had an immediate impact on the fitness fashion industry!
