Ariana Grande
Ariana Grande started out in the beauty industry with her first fragrance in 2015. Since then, the singer-songwriter has expanded her fragrance business. In 2021, Grande established R.E.M Excellence; The following year, she started releasing makeup collections in separate waves. Her excellence business developed with deliveries, for example, First Chapter: ultraviolet light, including cosmetics for the lips and eyes; Twond Chapter: Goodnight & Go, which included skincare, blush, and lashes in her line.
She has released a number of lines to rave reviews as of 2023, contributing significantly to her estimated net worth of $220 million. 